      "role": "林路",
      "timestamp": "10:03",
      "timestampManuallyEdited": true
    },
    {
      "content": "不回你是因为刚才在上课",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "林路"
    },
    {
      "content": "老师上课玩手机也太离谱了吧",
